ng":"G1223","grammar":"PREP","lemma":"διά","meaning":"through/because of"},{"word":"μέλανος","translit":"melanos","translation":"ink","strong":"G3188","grammar":"N-GSN","lemma":"μέλαν","meaning":"ink"},{"word":"καὶ","translit":"kai","translation":"and","strong":"G2532","grammar":"CONJ","lemma":"καί","meaning":"and"},{"word":"καλάμου","translit":"kalamou","translation":"pen","strong":"G2563","grammar":"N-GSM","lemma":"κάλαμος","meaning":"reed/stick/pen"},{"word":"σοι","translit":"soi","translation":"to you","strong":"G4771","grammar":"P-2DS","lemma":"σύ","meaning":"you"},{"word":"γράφειν·","translit":"graphein","translation":"to write;","strong":"G1125","grammar":"V-PAN","lemma":"γράφω","meaning":"to write"}],"14":[{"word":"ἐλπίζω","translit":"elpizō","translation":"I hope","strong":"G1679","grammar":"V-PAI-1S","lemma":"ἐλπίζω","meaning":"to hope/expect"},{"word":"δὲ","translit":"de","translation":"however","strong":"G1161","grammar":"CONJ","lemma":"δέ","meaning":"but/and"},{"word":"εὐθέως","translit":"eutheōs","translation":"soon","strong":"G2112","grammar":"ADV","lemma":"εὐθέως","meaning":"immediately"},{"word":"σε","translit":"se","translation":"you","strong":"G4771","grammar":"P-2AS","lemma":"σύ","meaning":"you"},{"word":"ἰδεῖν,","translit":"idein","translation":"to see","strong":"G1492H","grammar":"V-2AAN","lemma":"εἴδω","meaning":"to perceive"},{"word":"καὶ","translit":"kai","translation":"and","strong":"G2532","grammar":"CONJ","lemma":"καί","meaning":"and"},{"word":"στόμα","translit":"stoma","translation":"mouth","strong":"G4750","grammar":"N-ASN","lemma":"στόμα","meaning":"mouth"},{"word":"πρὸς","translit":"pros","translation":"to","strong":"G4314","grammar":"PREP","lemma":"πρός","meaning":"to/with"},{"word":"στόμα","translit":"stoma","translation":"mouth","strong":"G4750","grammar":"N-ASN","lemma":"στόμα","meaning":"mouth"},{"word":"λαλήσομεν.","translit":"lalēsomen","translation":"we will speak.","strong":"G2980","grammar":"V-FAI-1P","lemma":"λαλέω","meaning":"to speak"}],"15":[{"word":"εἰρήνη","translit":"eirēnē","translation":"Peace","strong":"G1515","grammar":"N-NSF","lemma":"εἰρήνη","meaning":"peace"},{"word":"σοι.","translit":"soi","translation":"to you.","strong":"G4771","grammar":"P-2DS","lemma":"σύ","meaning":"you"},{"word":"ἀσπάζονταί","translit":"aspazontai","translation":"Greet","strong":"G0782","grammar":"V-PNI-3P","lemma":"ἀσπάζομαι","meaning":"to pay respects to"},{"word":"σε","translit":"se","translation":"you","strong":"G4771","grammar":"P-2AS","lemma":"σύ","meaning":"you"},{"word":"οἱ","translit":"hoi","translation":"the","strong":"G3588","grammar":"T-NPM","lemma":"ὁ","meaning":"the/this/who"},{"word":"φίλοι.","translit":"philoi","translation":"friends.","strong":"G5384","grammar":"A-NPM","lemma":"φίλος","meaning":"friendly/friend "},{"word":"ἀσπάζου","translit":"aspazou","translation":"do greet","strong":"G0782","grammar":"V-PNM-2S","lemma":"ἀσπάζομαι","meaning":"to pay respects to"},{"word":"τοὺς","translit":"tous","translation":"the","strong":"G3588","grammar":"T-APM","lemma":"ὁ","meaning":"the/this/who"},{"word":"φίλους","translit":"philous","translation":"friends","strong":"G5384","grammar":"A-APM","lemma":"φίλος","meaning":"friendly/friend "},{"word":"κατ᾽","translit":"kat᾽","translation":"by","strong":"G2596","grammar":"PREP","lemma":"κατά","meaning":"according to"},{"word":"ὄνομα.¶","translit":"onoma","translation":"name.","strong":"G3686","grammar":"N-ASN","lemma":"ὄνομα","meaning":"name"}]}},"krv":{"3JN_1_1":"장로는 사랑하는 가이오 곧 나의 참으로 사랑하는 자에게 편지하노라","3JN_1_2":"사랑하는 자여 네 영혼이 잘됨 같이 네가 범사에 잘되고 강건하기를 내가 간구하노라","3JN_1_3":"형제들이 와서 네게 있는 진리를 증거하되 네가 진리 안에서 행한다 하니 내가 심히 기뻐하노라","3JN_1_4":"내가 내 자녀들이 진리 안에서 행한다 함을 듣는 것보다 더 즐거움이 없도다","3JN_1_5":"사랑하는 자여 네가 무엇이든지 형제 곧 나그네 된 자들에게 행하는 것이 신실한 일이니","3JN_1_6":"저희가 교회 앞에서 너의 사랑을 증거하였느니라 네가 하나님께 합당하게 저희를 전송하면 가하리로다","3JN_1_7":"이는 저희가 주의 이름을 위하여 나가서 이방인에게 아무 것도 받지 아니함이라","3JN_1_8":"이러므로 우리가 이같은 자들을 영접하는 것이 마땅하니 이는 우리로 진리를 위하여 함께 수고하는 자가 되게 하려 함이니라","3JN_1_9":"내가 두어 자를 교회에게 썼으나 저희 중에 으뜸되기를 좋아하는 디오드레베가 우리를 접대하지 아니하니","3JN_1_10":"이러므로 내가 가면 그 행한 일을 잊지 아니하리라 저가 악한 말로 우리를 망령되이 폄론하고도 유위부족하여 형제들을 접대치도 아니하고 접대하고자 하는 자를 금하여 교회에서 내어 쫓는도다","3JN_1_11":"사랑하는 자여 악한 것을 본받지 말고 선한 것을 본받으라 선을 행하는 자는 하나님께 속하고 악을 행하는 자는 하나님을 뵈옵지 못하였느니라","3JN_1_12":"데메드리오는 뭇사람에게도, 진리에게도 증거를 받았으매 우리도 증거하노니 너는 우리의 증거가 참된 줄을 아느니라","3JN_1_13":"내가 네게 쓸 것이 많으나 먹과 붓으로 쓰기를 원치 아니하고","3JN_1_14":"속히 보기를 바라노니 또한 우리가 면대하여 말하리라","3JN_1_15":"평강이 네게 있을지어다 여러 친구가 네게 문안하느니라 너는 각 친구 명하에 문안하라"},"kjv":{},"net":{"3JN_1_1":"From the elder, to Gaius my dear brother, whom I love in truth.","3JN_1_2":"Dear friend, I pray that all may go well with you and that you may be in good health, just as it is well with your soul.","3JN_1_3":"For I rejoiced greatly when the brothers came and testified to your truth, just as you are living according to the truth.","3JN_1_4":"I have no greater joy than this: to hear that my children are living according to the truth. The Charge to Gaius","3JN_1_5":"Dear friend, you demonstrate faithfulness by whatever you do for the brothers (even though they are strangers).","3JN_1_6":"They have testified to your love before the church. You will do well to send them on their way in a manner worthy of God.","3JN_1_7":"For they have gone forth on behalf of “The Name,” accepting nothing from the pagans.","3JN_1_8":"Therefore we ought to support such people, so that we become coworkers in cooperation with the truth. Diotrephes the Troublemaker","3JN_1_9":"I wrote something to the church, but Diotrephes, who loves to be first among them, does not acknowledge us.","3JN_1_10":"Therefore, if I come, I will call attention to the deeds he is doing —the bringing of unjustified charges against us with evil words! And not being content with that, he not only refuses to welcome the brothers himself, but hinders the people who want to do so and throws them out of the church!","3JN_1_11":"Dear friend, do not imitate what is bad but what is good. The one who does good is of God; the one who does what is bad has not seen God. Worthy Demetrius","3JN_1_12":"Demetrius has been testified to by all, even by the truth itself. We also testify to him, and you know that our testimony is true. Conclusion","3JN_1_13":"I have many things to write to you, but I do not wish to write to you with pen and ink.","3JN_1_14":"But I hope to see you right away, and we will speak face to face.","3JN_1_15":"Peace be with you. The friends here greet you. Greet the friends there by name."}}